---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="About | NetOps OS">
  <Header />
  <main class="page">
    <p class="label">About</p>
    <h1>About NetOps OS</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      NetOps OS is a long-term initiative to build a practical Network Operations Workbench for engineers, infrastructure teams, NOC teams, managed service providers, and students.
    </p>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <article class="card"><h3>Mission</h3><p>Reduce operational complexity by bringing essential NetOps workflows into one structured workbench.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Audience</h3><p>Designed for network engineers, infrastructure engineers, system administrators, NOC teams, and learners.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Direction</h3><p>The project will start small, then evolve into a modular, vendor-neutral control center.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Repository</h3><p>Development and public progress will be tracked on GitHub.</p></article>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</MainLayout>
